like there's no point.

1052
01:24:03,520 --> 01:24:07,650
And I just stuck up for him
all the time. (SNIFFLING)

1053
01:24:07,800 --> 01:24:10,929
'Cause it wasn't his fault. It was mine.

1054
01:24:13,960 --> 01:24:16,611
