1149
01:33:33,920 --> 01:33:36,764
(ALL CHEERING)

1150
01:33:40,600 --> 01:33:43,410
(CROWD CHEERING, APPLAUDING)

1151
01:33:45,520 --> 01:33:48,000
- Oh, there's your precious Angel Cake.
- What did I tell you, buddy?

1152
01:33:48,160 --> 01:33:50,891
